(secondQuint)Multimedia Information and Pre-operative Anxiety.

 To determine whether multimedia information reduces the level of pre-operative anxiety in patients undergoing major elective surgery.

 To evaluate the efficacy of a video, showing the patient pathway to and from the Operating Theatre, compared with standard information, a written leaflet, about the operating room experience and environment.

